            <h2>the story</h2>
            <p>The story follows Aloy, a young hunter in a world dominated by robotic creatures. Raised by her guardian Rost, she embarks on a quest to discover her origins and the truth behind the machines. As she explores the vast open world, she encounters various tribes, uncovers ancient technologies, and battles formidable foes.</p>
            
